+# Architecture guardrail allowlist.
+#
+# Format: source-relative-path=max_raw_commands_spawn_count
+#
+# These are known legacy raw spawn sites in room-feature spawn modules. New
+# room-authored spawns should use platformer_runtime lifecycle helpers instead
+# of increasing these counts.
+content/features/ecs/spawn.rs=0
+content/features/ecs/spawn_actors.rs=3
+content/features/ecs/spawn_mounts.rs=0
+content/features/ecs/spawn_static.rs=0
